Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.35,0:00:11.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然我還是寫不出來
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.25,0:00:12.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是姐姐自己說的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.85,0:00:16.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在本人面前無法坦率  所以才寫情書的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.15,0:00:18.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話是這麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.55,0:00:21.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但真到寫的時候  卻不知道該寫些什麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.62,0:00:23.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我來幫你寫吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.00,0:00:26.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…紗伊阿九斗君
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.20,0:00:29.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每當我見到你  總是說些刻薄的話
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.60,0:00:33.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是啊  其實我最喜歡你了  這就是傲嬌啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.72,0:00:36.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能理解我的心情嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.30,0:00:40.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}阿九斗君的話一定能理解我的吧（愛心）
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.27,0:00:40.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光是聽著就渾身起雞皮疙瘩
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.09,0:00:43.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最喜歡你了  熱戀著你的服部絢子  寫完啦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.99,0:00:44.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.27,0:00:46.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不寫了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.56,0:00:50.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這東西我就收下了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.34,0:00:51.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,照屋榮子
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.36,0:00:52.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.72,0:00:57.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把這個大量複製之後  在學校裡散發
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.79,0:00:59.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣你就顏面掃地了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.99,0:01:01.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼！？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.17,0:01:04.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是寧靜的假日啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.34,0:01:07.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種日子就要好好地…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.14,0:01:07.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站住！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.13,0:01:11.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你當我是說站住就站住的笨蛋啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.33,0:01:12.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呼…呼吸…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.72,0:01:15.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…真是的…不要亂動啦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.64,0:01:16.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點還給我
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.76,0:01:19.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.11,0:01:22.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還想逃嗎  你這個混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.64,0:01:25.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您升天了嗎  在各種意義上
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.67,0:01:27.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真…真下流
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.34,0:01:29.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  手卷？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.06,0:01:30.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為是忍者
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.61,0:01:34.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站住  你這個不知羞恥的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.36,0:01:34.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是煩人啊  這樣的話
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.88,0:01:35.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一決勝負吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.11,0:01:43.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來是平手啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.53,0:01:44.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.09,0:01:45.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.63,0:01:49.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,輸…輸了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.52,0:01:51.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  把手卷還給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.43,0:01:53.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.46,0:01:54.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  不見了？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.35,0:01:57.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像在哪裡弄丟了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.13,0:01:58.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼！？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.95,0:02:00.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要  要是被他看到的話
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.02,0:02:02.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那才真是…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.98,0:02:05.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寫著什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.42,0:02:06.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等  等等
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.42,0:02:09.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是很重要的文件
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.88,0:02:12.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該怎麼說呢…不能讓那傢伙奪走…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.32,0:02:13.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起這個  你的衣服…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.48,0:02:13.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.29,0:02:17.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我居然穿成這樣滿學校亂跑…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.68,0:02:21.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.42,0:02:41.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說小阿  你喜歡大的還是小的？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.36,0:02:42.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？  大的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.67,0:02:44.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,堅挺的還是柔軟的？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.24,0:02:45.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柔軟的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.69,0:02:48.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此啊  小阿也和大家一樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.67,0:02:50.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集  惠奈的愛之圍裙！？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.97,0:02:52.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,變得這麼大了
